{"tid":2488569,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紫荊研究院 微信調查: 八成半受訪市民認為《港區國安法》不影響生活","createTime":"2021-04-14T10:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:42:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8c17c640a25d3575ad7a0446369fa30188d37ee6","tid":2488569,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"調查在4月8日至13日期間，以<span class=\"red\">音頻電話</span>隨機抽樣形式進行，在1,528名受訪市民中，85.7%受訪者認同香港有維護國家安全的憲制責任，較去年5月國安法實施前所做同類調查相比，大幅攀升超過兩成。<br />\n<br />\n打飛機結論:<br />\n研究院又指，《港區國安法》實施之初，許多市民持觀望和疑懼態度，不少反對者更趁機鼓躁，刻意歪曲。然而，九個多月過去後，任何人只要不懷偏見、不戴有色眼鏡，都能感受到《港區國安法》在將香港社會重新帶回發展正軌中發揮的積極作用，「一法定香江」已成為過去九個多月最好的寫照。"},{"pid":"602c7b46f846da0b648feba7f11590573d15fe76","tid":2488569,"uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"音頻調查不能作準 : 鍾庭耀<br />\n<br />\n（一）音頻電話訪問調查的成功率極度偏低，與專業民意調查的要求相去甚遠，願意接受訪問的人士極可能只屬於某特定社經背景人士，使得所取得的樣本缺乏代表性。<br />\n<br />\n（二）音頻電話訪問無法透過訪問員的直接詢問和判斷選擇適合的受訪者，進一步減低了樣本的有效性。<br />\n<br />\n（三）音頻電話訪問甚少對受訪者的背景資料作出詳細詢問，使得其調查樣本難以與整體人口比較，以便確定有關樣本是否偏離調查所推論的整體人口分佈結構。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/columns/columns91.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkupop.hku.hk%2Fchinese%2Fcolumns%2Fcolumns91.html&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=4d829859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/columns/columns91.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a886a5fcde23f4666c24fe11d45d0b4d3ed6099","tid":2488569,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c51ac19b03172d423033a977005053da08e5ab8","tid":2488569,"uid":60470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"陰貧電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fa2c7e70f89deb25b79c9dc4708ef0b057969d","tid":2488569,"uid":18948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"連微訊都有15% 反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23315841fbc0778c982dc0f56e33815cc73ec258","tid":2488569,"uid":37586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"信就信,唔信就唔信,乜撚野微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用得支那app嘅咪支持支那班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a9c78d7501fcffa9ee067d6f64668758978172","tid":2488569,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"仲有一成班藍屍頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f571f83266bb1eadd570b66ed52eaeb388bab7","tid":2488569,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5fa2c7e70f89deb25b79c9dc4708ef0b057969d","tid":2488569,"uid":18948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"連微訊都有15% 反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"嗰15%應該捉去坐監"},{"pid":"48190f819644ebde8e37b79635556353f086adc5","tid":2488569,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"點會唔影響生活呀<br />\n<br />\n明明國家安全咗、生活好咗、搵到工賺大錢、大灣區樓價升、頭髮都濃密咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fb447dfa6cea86397edf9362074023f1e058f0","tid":2488569,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675618961d22356a849ff3a39dd0a218852aaa91","tid":2488569,"uid":56115